org.zebrafish.feature
Interface Feature

All Known Subinterfaces:
FieldList<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractFeature, AbstractFieldList, AbstractFillList, AxisList, BarWidth, ColorList, DataList, DataScaleList, GradientFillList, Grid, LegendList, LegendPositionList, LineStyleList, MarkerList, PieLegendList, SolidFillList, StripeFillList, Title
public interface Feature

A feature which can be added into charts. Usually every feature presents a parameter in URL query strings.

Method Detail

createStringBuffer

java.lang.StringBuffer createStringBuffer()
Creates a StringBuffer object which has appended parameter information in the head of the string. For instance, it will return a StringBuffer object which starts with "&chtt=" if the parameter name of this feature is "chtt".

Returns:
a StringBuffer object which has appended parameter information
